data.description: LOW TAXES ::GREAT PLACE TO LIVE >HOME ON PERMANENT FOUNDATION: QUALITY BUILT BY SILVER CREST. RETIRE in this beautifully established and vibrant 55+ community of Spring Knolls right in the heart of Murrieta. Upcoming Murrieta Hot Springs Spa & Resort,  Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, and high-quality medical facilities as well as local entertainment centers. The low monthly HOA includes access to resort style swimming pools, outdoor barbecues, bocce ball courts, a library, pool tables, a dog park, this community will keep you active Inside, this wonderful home boasts 3 bedrooms all good size, large master bedroom includes a Large soaking tub walk-in shower for easy accessibility, The indoor laundry washer/dryer and refrigerator are included in the sale. A wheelchair ramp A side covered carport fits three vehicles. Call to set up an appointment and visit your new home soon. where you can enjoy class amenities just minutes from your home. Located on a quiet street, low taxes,  You will love  living here
